            {
               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><img src=\"images/UniversityJohannesburg/ShonaJohannnesburg.jpg\" id=\"imgShona\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgShona', '0%')\" class=\"imgcenter\"/><b>Figure 2</b>: Photos of the Shona kitchen. At the top left, we see a photo of the kitchen with the door closed. At the top right, we see the back of the kitchen. At the bottom, there are images of the interior of the building. These photos were taken by Brian Z. Muratu (<htcite0>) and are being used under the terms defined by the University of Johannesburg, which shared the dissertation under the <a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/\" target=\"_blank\">Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike</a> license.</p>",
